# OpenBot Track Building Instructions

## Overview
These instructions will guide you in creating a modular and customizable OpenBot track complete with roads.

## Required Materials
### Base Platform
- 10x Corrugated Plastic Sheets (530mm x 760mm x 3mm) ([US](https://www.amazon.com/dp/B08C9S9XFJ/?mr_donotredirect=undefined&th=1), [EU](https://www.amazon.co.uk/Corrugated-Plastic-Outdoor-Waterproof-Coroplast/dp/B0CXCX684S/ref=sr_1_33?dib=eyJ2IjoiMSJ9.qxDcKr-bIssyror76QR25zwVhHfoXiv_69JdU1qLB_h7KHJ6AbzDy35rQDBmeEErshpSuW2MgaD-96we9Xou-9-tiCoDqbz3mOsvLk3vu8SDmWN7XUN9N3dZQo5mBD1rbTQcvlNwGIEWRJS8xr2FBCtXzE40PPJ-gF3RFl9CHtV2vB9sVT0hsvRvQSnJmgqL1Zr9hNc0ORVr7E_5TyqZCg9BzYVOjEBO17quffB368B4lZ3czD4DBDH0_x4rFEvKCBQwkDyLPhRgNKRS_TT8qYVvQ96pZioXSLzKDcWL4OOUstFqym6vOfiv0xftV0DKeLxPW5IyNlP75RA56PH7y_P9tI3JIIeWM5DlvzwOp-hqX5HYSHGFOrUDuFYvHhWTrl2EyCoicjNNmThiwVPAhDTMqEttXmb_OaPM3VEoedMK14cgQTnHcBxtCASl0Kgj.cRMT8sWsb09UfjY0p6A54jI05M71OFk2c4vSODMJIeE&dib_tag=se&keywords=corrugated%2Bplastic%2Bsheets%2B53cm%2Bx%2B76cm&nsdOptOutParam=true&qid=1736752683&sr=8-33&th=1), [ASIA](https://www.amazon.com/dp/B08C9S9XFJ/?mr_donotredirect=undefined&th=1))

### Cutting Tool
- 1x Utility Knife or Scissors ([US](https://www.amazon.com/WORKPRO-Premium-Utility-Retractable-Duty-Box/dp/B097SXK3FG/ref=sr_1_5?crid=2LUJDZYMX7D2N&dib=eyJ2IjoiMSJ9.isFFStTE3NuIVJ4J9vzXcDFSf4tzzSFuwMPCI3b8L8Z1AxWCelUdx6SKFPe1JPd5-gM-0ON170CphwJ0c-LTgKKCGaYEAdrbHgW7WqrHs2AIrsYyUb-FuihIi8k4lYI3fLX-hLfe8iEs3F8akZJnNljhS0oKhMMYrkD_npUCxIUaXNdyWVyYzJJe-AZ9Hy2VceQjfqIjg8weawJgxkuov4qYDdWhc8Rm_G6FhqWkenbh8gVjfBwcTxjBVwzkBCj7AggOJKIPHuJiDht3na_MDzgP7Jzv1jfIxXX-S1nOf_6zf2aj6LOT8eLzvoxANYj6K6U8LXbOIVtlx-n8IXGjLRZSvHsGN3xUp7Vb5ViEa6bDxtPcWLAeWG-6BeHimJH_sxJbtuCJhPPOHtk7uT1vxRwzh-0RaD6264rSfPjyEWoNu48YM1ZMttdCPkAvxkC2.ZBEnl1Ts6MBr1obFR4i-69n2rF0cKy25ARzlCUH_evc&dib_tag=se&keywords=utility%2Bknife&qid=1739244318&sprefix=utility%2Bkn%2Caps%2C389&sr=8-5&th=1), [EU](https://www.amazon.co.uk/AmazonBasics-Folding-Utility-Lightweight-Aluminium/dp/B07TBNH4ZT/ref=sr_1_1_ffob_sspa?crid=3TXLBBKPRUDH1&dib=eyJ2IjoiMSJ9.OIu8nFQrPwJOJmu0BTfFTBhbAIwO1k05X6qsgXzhMDnHJhDvh1s2_4pE30AbQWbOsYcyJkdWXd4kkukWKZBVoXIVTB2W_m2wUk7myNaeYx2I3IirJ62yngU_WqHhMl-2eJ7ct_JB9quHVY_yfPoeBRYTQRlmGYNLkt8Fdie3FbcnAQ3rHESueAlpz5YEiItFGzcFisqRH4U7Tl2e3rNIedBc8YYQLAjsSNfbmfuSsPNGzP2M4T-B-E0QFk2VGqlCMdenNa29d22wLoP0jPEhS1iMf2ACHt63U_Klb9-08-s.js9prflsfWqvS8QD9rMZrNZeO6GCDVshSzSaAE8k848&dib_tag=se&keywords=Utility+knife&qid=1739244546&sprefix=utility+kn%2Caps%2C271&sr=8-1-spons&sp_csd=d2lkZ2V0TmFtZT1zcF9hdGY&psc=1), [ASIA](https://www.amazon.com/WORKPRO-Premium-Utility-Retractable-Duty-Box/dp/B097SXK3FG/ref=sr_1_5?crid=2LUJDZYMX7D2N&dib=eyJ2IjoiMSJ9.isFFStTE3NuIVJ4J9vzXcDFSf4tzzSFuwMPCI3b8L8Z1AxWCelUdx6SKFPe1JPd5-gM-0ON170CphwJ0c-LTgKKCGaYEAdrbHgW7WqrHs2AIrsYyUb-FuihIi8k4lYI3fLX-hLfe8iEs3F8akZJnNljhS0oKhMMYrkD_npUCxIUaXNdyWVyYzJJe-AZ9Hy2VceQjfqIjg8weawJgxkuov4qYDdWhc8Rm_G6FhqWkenbh8gVjfBwcTxjBVwzkBCj7AggOJKIPHuJiDht3na_MDzgP7Jzv1jfIxXX-S1nOf_6zf2aj6LOT8eLzvoxANYj6K6U8LXbOIVtlx-n8IXGjLRZSvHsGN3xUp7Vb5ViEa6bDxtPcWLAeWG-6BeHimJH_sxJbtuCJhPPOHtk7uT1vxRwzh-0RaD6264rSfPjyEWoNu48YM1ZMttdCPkAvxkC2.ZBEnl1Ts6MBr1obFR4i-69n2rF0cKy